  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="last-updated">Last updated: June 16, 2025</p>

  <p>This privacy policy applies to all mobile and web applications developed and published by <strong>AppMint-AI Limited</strong>, including but not limited to MyCabby, GymBuddy, and any future products under the AppMint-AI brand.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, and login credentials</li>
    <li><strong>Device & Usage Info:</strong> Device type, operating system, app version, usage analytics</li>
    <li><strong>App-Specific Data:</strong> Depending on the app, this may include location, fitness activity, expenses, or uploaded content (e.g., receipts or workouts)</li>
    <li><strong>Optional Inputs:</strong> Voice commands, biometric info, or media uploads — only when explicitly enabled</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To operate and improve our apps and services</li>
    <li>To personalize user experience</li>
    <li>To fulfill legal and regulatory obligations (e.g. tax reporting via MyCabby)</li>
    <li>To provide customer support and account maintenance</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>With third-party services (e.g. hosting, analytics) under strict data protection agreements</li>
    <li>With government authorities only when legally required or with your explicit consent</li>
    <li>Never sold to advertisers or data brokers</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>End-to-end encryption</li>
    <li>Secure servers and cloud storage</li>
    <li>Role-based access and internal audits</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Under GDPR and UK data protection law, you can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Request access or deletion of your data</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent</li>
    <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
    <li>Object to processing or request data portability</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>We retain data as long as needed to provide the service or comply with regulations</li>
    <li>Financial data is retained for 6 years (if applicable)</li>
    <li>You may request deletion at any time</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>Our apps are not intended for children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect their data.</p>

  <h2>8. Changes</h2>
  <p>This policy may be updated periodically. Material changes will be notified via app or email.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Company:</strong> AppMint-AI Limited</li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@appmint.ai</li>
    <li><strong>DPO:</strong> dpo@appmint.ai</li>
    <li><strong>Registered Address:</strong> 123 Business Street, London, UK</li>
  </ul>
